          "tz": 120
        },
        "subject": "LU-3941 lov: only modify extent of sub-lock and preserve flags",
        "message": "LU-3941 lov: only modify extent of sub-lock and preserve flags\n\nIf Glimpse-lock's sub-locks have to be modifed, only update\nextent datas and preserve others originl fields, particularly\ncld_enq_flags to ensure CEF_ASYNC flag will be kept and no\nconflict detection will wrongly occur.\n\nThis is b2_1 version of Gerrit-change #7569, with Change-Id\nI599da98ce364ccf459b5b5f3b72550115972c456, for LU-3027 and LU-3874.\n\nTest-Parameters: envdefinitions=SLOW=yes,ENABLE_QUOTA=yes mdtcount=1 \ttestlist=parallel-scale,parallel-scale-nfsv3,parallel-scale-nfsv4\nSigned-off-by: Bruno Faccini <bruno.faccini@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I5c4ba501d0cb67b1c83a8993e548bf1e17ad714a\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_1"
    }
